originalText.text: This place is an absolute scam. The doctor walked in and without even examining me or asking questions about my condition, and told me I would need laser surgery. When I asked her to explain further, she backed up and just repeated herself slowly, not addressing concerns, or alternative options. Was extremely defensive and not informative. Will absolutely not be coming back.

originalText.text: An absolute scam of a place. They will charge you for procedures that you were unaware of and did not ask for. I was charged for "Acne Surgery" which were just unnecessary and painful extractions that both deeply scarred and hyperpigmented my face. Do not go here if you value your time, money, and skin.
